Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 帮我拿酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来伸出手不就拿到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就不用酱油了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这紧张兮兮的气氛是怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷不知道你在那边发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过难得大家一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能开心一点嘛 怎么样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 好冷哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子她妈 她到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 茶叶梗立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远隔万里而相通的二人之心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像已经好久没有来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由加 绘理 步美 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你怎么还这么悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你得了economy class症候群请假的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}economy class症候群：实际上不存在这种疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么乱七八糟的症候群啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷又学会新的病名了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩是一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间总是缠着北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学好像也不是很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么办？这不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不管可是会被抢走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方才一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤又这么光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是北条同学那样的男生最喜欢的类型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我又没在跟北条同学交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然另外有男朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能会表现得这么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我光是想起他就一肚子火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在怀疑我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你刚才一直是那样看我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要冲我发脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是你自己有那种奇怪的误会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到你这张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你去哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去钢牙那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是一口古井而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里跟戈薇的国家连在一起的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是能通过古井的只有戈薇和犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有犬夜叉能去接戈薇回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只没大脑的笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不知道在赌什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有人在背后说我坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 有人说你坏话也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的确干了那么多蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老太婆 你说我做了什么蠢事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋就是笨蛋 无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要找出四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的灵力是不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把她给气回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是她自己擅自跑回去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么“我要回家了 笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你学戈薇一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情有什么所谓嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 请大家排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 姑娘的手相不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后会很长寿而且子孙满堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人 是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意为我生个孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人你好讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人刚才也跟我说了一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要看到美女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就忍不住想要对方为我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这么看来似乎有点苗头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道我能不能一次满足你们二位呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人好讨厌哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是老头子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们现在怎么急也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非犬夜叉能够好好冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我们几个根本是无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉笨得无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上他的脾气又臭又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后最好不要靠近枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想想犬夜叉的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发现有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他想去接戈薇小姐也去不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙与表面相反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心也有很可爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼前就有个最好的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 没人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那家伙 我还是无法原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对 要让她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这次你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在跟什么样的男生交往啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个小气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野蛮任性又暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是个超～级醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果爱吃醋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就表示他很喜欢戈薇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会更有趣点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人对戈薇很专情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话我也没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没办法忘记以前喜欢过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都犹豫不决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛 仔细想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉明明是喜欢桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要因为我吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇受到了很猛烈的追求对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还想杀了接近我的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你为什么要跟那种人交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须跟他分手 绝对不能再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是野蛮又任性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还脚踏两条船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是他也有优点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人很温柔 而且很强大很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是喜欢他吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢…？我喜欢犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定是喜欢他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…充满了戈薇的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戈薇姐姐的弟弟 叫草太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来玩的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们没有吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在生气啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人真爱计较
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么突然觉得好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 狗狗哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要告诉戈薇我到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是男人之间的约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人之间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么随便进别人的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…这是男人之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时犬夜叉这么辛苦跑来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却站在钢牙那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…是我不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会向她道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底去干什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人操心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你自己说不准我们靠近枯井的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情就是要观看过程才好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到学校里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病已经好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们最近都没时间好好谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该回去比较好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你周六没空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会去吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 周六见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们干嘛擅自帮我决定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像北条同学这样正常的男人才适合戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟那个醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又花心 还有暴力倾向的男生交往下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的将来会很悲惨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在说犬夜叉吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 你一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉还在生气吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本来就很顽固的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到你那张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊…现在回去的话可能又要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…不要突然冒出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶紧去接她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是好像是我错了一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是你不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在怀疑戈薇是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说要决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是那种时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙受伤了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇确实保护了钢牙让他逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道钢牙是犬夜叉的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且戈薇还不计较自己被他劫持并遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 明明最受钢牙欺负的是戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她还要帮钢牙啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇说不定真的喜欢上了钢牙对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要劝人家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先想好一套说词再来行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在给我滚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 犬夜叉 刚才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了 你真的是很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过不去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就绝对不会去接她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 你先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这种麻烦的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找人生经验丰富的枫姥姥商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是最好的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心 我不会说出你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就假装是要问我朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是可以稍微听你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 只…只是稍微哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 我是帮我一个狗狗朋友来找你商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 你那个狗朋友怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个狗狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢上一只猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了一匹野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对猫咪一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗与野狼每次见面都会打架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼 从狗狗身边抢走了猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是仇恨野狼的妖怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后赶来救猫咪的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使消灭了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗想把受伤的野狼也一并收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪却保护了野狼 让他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪只是保护了受伤的野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗却怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪是不是喜欢上那只野狼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后猫咪就生气地回到了自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 事情大概就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让狗狗和猫咪和好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先狗要承认自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你激动什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是在说七宝的狗朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 猫咪可能等狗狗去接她等得都不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这两个人都误会了对方所以无法和好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要让两个人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是解决问题最快捷的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你还要在这边待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 我不能在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在学业繁忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能总是跑去战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就总是跑去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为犬夜叉会来带我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能已经不会来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是姐姐一直在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不来的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在生气…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一早再起来念书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在根本集中不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被子好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边根本就睡不舒服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会替我值夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…他在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦话？她梦到我了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这臭丫头到底在做什么梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹钟不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…是犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以周六不能陪你去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别介意我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那个一年级的女孩子去看电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺喜欢北条同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真傻 原来你是在意那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不打算跟别的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我有点高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮原来因为我在吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我下次再约你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学真坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也能像那样自信满满的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正犬夜叉不会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我稍微向他低头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在生气对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到犬夜叉会这么老实地向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真的不生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你说是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为你弄坏了这个闹钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你以为还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉其实是在反省的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还去了你那边两次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从戈薇走了以后 他就一直在叹气…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们不要多嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道我去那边了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 既然已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就先老实道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰唆！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我们吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不干呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是担心你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要你们多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我必须要道歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真激动啊 因为他高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇回来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是我的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样…风穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事就吸我进去！
